                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18011028-9-defend112 t18011028-9-punish55"></join>
               confined six months in the House of Correction
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice Heath.</p>
